@page "/about"
<PageTitle>About · D365 ERP Command Center</PageTitle>

<div class="page-header">
    <div>
        <h1>About this project</h1>
    </div>
</div>

<p class="lead">
    The D365 ERP Command Center is a self-contained Blazor WebAssembly portfolio demo built by
    Keystone Marcy. It models <strong>Alamo Foods Co.</strong>, a fictional San Antonio food
    manufacturer in the middle of a Microsoft Dynamics 365 Finance &amp; Operations roll-out.
    Everything runs entirely client-side in your browser — there is no server or database. The
    sample data is seeded into <code>localStorage</code> on first load, so you can browse,
    edit and explore freely.
</p>

